{"title":"键盘控制&控制台打印数据(以C语言为例)","uid":"b44f2b4c0ef151e2d4963b4e3c1a4d2e","slug":"Webots/Application/键盘控制&控制台打印数据(以C语言为例)","date":"2022-01-30T12:49:36.000Z","updated":"2022-02-08T16:30:33.718Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Webots/Application/键盘控制&控制台打印数据(以C语言为例).json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://s2.loli.net/2022/02/08/8AXxcNfEyh5GuCl.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"1-键盘控制\"><a href=\"#1-键盘控制\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.键盘控制\"></a><strong>1.键盘控制</strong></h1><p>官方对于键盘有详细的解释</p>\n<p>我们常用就是以下函数，以及使用键盘控制时需要包含的头文件</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c\" data-language=\"c\"><code class=\"language-c\">#include &lt;webots&#x2F;keyboard.h&gt;\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F;使能键盘控制\nvoid wb_keyboard_enable(int sampling_period);\n&#x2F;&#x2F;失能键盘控制\nvoid wb_keyboard_disable();\n&#x2F;&#x2F;获取键盘控制采样时间\nint wb_keyboard_get_sampling_period();\n&#x2F;&#x2F;获取键盘按键\nint wb_keyboard_get_key();</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"1-1-使用方法\"><a href=\"#1-1-使用方法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.1. 使用方法\"></a>1.1. 使用方法</h2><ul>\n<li><p>包含头文件</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c\" data-language=\"c\"><code class=\"language-c\">#include &lt;webots&#x2F;keyboard.h&gt;</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>在循环外使能键盘控制</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c\" data-language=\"c\"><code class=\"language-c\">wb_keyboard_enable(TIME_STEP);</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>循环内获取键盘按键，存储到变量中</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c\" data-language=\"c\"><code class=\"language-c\">int key &#x3D; wb_keyboard_get_key();</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>判断获取了键盘按键</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c\" data-language=\"c\"><code class=\"language-c\">switch (key)\n    &#123;\n    case &#39;A&#39;:\n      Vx &#x3D; 0.0f;\n      VOmega &#x3D; -5.0f;\n     break;\n   case &#39;D&#39;:\n      Vx &#x3D; 0.0f;\n     VOmega &#x3D; 5.0f;\n     break;\n   case &#39;S&#39;:\n     Vx &#x3D; -5.0f;\n     VOmega &#x3D; 0.0f;\n      break;\n    case &#39;W&#39;:\n     Vx &#x3D; 5.0f;\n     VOmega &#x3D; 0.0f;\n     break;\n   default:\n     Vx &#x3D; 0.0f;\n     VOmega &#x3D; 0.0f;\n    &#125;</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"2-控制台打印数据\"><a href=\"#2-控制台打印数据\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.控制台打印数据\"></a><strong>2.控制台打印数据</strong></h1><p>在旧版本是可以直接用printf来直接打印数据，但是新版本需要加上一句话才能打印</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c\" data-language=\"c\"><code class=\"language-c\">printf(&quot;%d\\n&quot;,key);\nfflush(stdout);</code></pre>\n\n<h1 id=\"参考与致谢\"><a href=\"#参考与致谢\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"参考与致谢\"></a><strong>参考与致谢</strong></h1><p><a href=\"https://cyberbotics.com/doc/reference/keyboard\">Webots 键盘使用</a></p>\n","text":"1.键盘控制官方对于键盘有详细的解释 我们常用就是以下函数，以及使用键盘控制时需要包含的头文件 #include &lt;webots&#x2F;keyboard.h&gt; &#x2F;&#x2F;使能键盘控制 void wb_keyboard_enable(int sampl...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"运动仿真","slug":"运动仿真","count":19,"path":"api/categories/运动仿真.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Webots","slug":"Webots","count":19,"path":"api/tags/Webots.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-%E9%94%AE%E7%9B%98%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1.键盘控制</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-1-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1.1. 使用方法</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%8F%B0%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.控制台打印数据</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83%E4%B8%8E%E8%87%B4%E8%B0%A2\"><span class=\"toc-text\">参考与致谢</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Miraggio","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://s2.loli.net/2022/01/23/kntF9TEBOyHquwV.png","link":"https://lapzjfit.site","description":"喜欢研究奇奇怪怪的技术&游戏宅","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","c